quran[20]{c,v,t}:
  25,1,Uyingcwele lowo owehlisela phansi isimo sokunquma phezu kwenceku yakhe ukuze ibe ngumxwayisi ezizweni
  25,2,Okunguyena okungowakhe umbuso wamazulu nomhlaba futhi ongakaze abe nendodana futhi ongenaye umhlanganyeli embusweni futhi wadala zonke izinto wazilinganisa ngendlela ezifaneleke ngayo
  25,3,Futhi bazithathela abanye onkulunkulu esikhundleni sakhe abangakwazi ukudala lutho kulapho bona bedaliwe futhi bona uqobo lwabo abanalutho olulimazayo futhi abanalutho oluyinzuzo futhi abakwazi ukudala ukufa nokupha impilo nokuvusa (abafileyo)
  25,4,"Futhi labo abangakholwanga bathi, “lokhu akuyilutho ngaphandle kwamanga awaqambile futhi abanye abantu bamelekelela kuwo ngakho-ke ngempela baveze okungenabulungiswa nokungaimanga”"
  25,5,"Futhi bathi, “yizinganekwane zasendulo azibhale phansi ngakho-ke uyabizelwa zona ekuseni nakusihlwa”"
  25,6,"Ithi, “uyehlisele phansi lowo owazi imfihlo emazulwini nasemhlabeni ngempela yena ngasosonke isikhathi uyathethelela unesihawu”"
  25,7,"Futhi bathi, “kungani lesisithunywa sidla ukudla futhi siyahamba siya ezitolo na? Kungani kungehliselwanga phansi kusona ingelosi ukuze ibe ngumxwayisi kanye naso”"
  25,8,Noma anikezwe ingcebo noma abe nesivande adla kusona futhi abayizoni bathi “anilandeli lutho ngaphandle komuntu olunjiwe”
  25,9,Bheka ukuthi bakwenzela kanjani izibonelo base beyaduka bangakwazi ukuyifumana indlela
  25,10,Uyingcwele lowo othi uma ethanda akubekele okungcono kunalokho – izivande okugeleza ngaphansi kwazo imifula futhi uzokubekela izindlu ezinkulu zobukhosi
  25,11,Kepha bayaliphika ihora futhi noma ngabe nguba oliphikayo ihora simlungiselele umlilo ovuthayo
  25,12,Uma ubabona (umlilo) besendaweni ekude bayokuzwa ulaka olukhulu nokubhonga kwawo
  25,13,Futhi uma bephonswa endaweni encane ngobubanzi lapho phakathi beboshwe ngamaketango bayokhalela ukubhujiswa lapho
  25,14,Musani namhlanje ukukhalela ukubhujiswa okukodwa kepha khalelani ukubhujiswa okuningi
  25,15,"Ithi, “ngakubelokhokungcononomaisivandesangunaphakade okuyisona esathenjiswa abagwema okubi na? Lokho ngumvuzo nesiphetho sabo”"
  25,16,"Okwabo lapho phakathi kuyoba yikona konke lokho abakufisayo, bayohlalakhonaingunaphakade, lesiyisethembiso ukugcwaliseka kwaso kuseNkosini yakho"
  25,17,"Futhi ngosuku lapho eyobaqoqa ngalo kanye nalokho abakukhonzayo esikhundleni sikaMvelinqangi bese ethi, “ngakube nina naziphambukisa yini lezizinceku zami noma zona zaziphambukela ngokwazo endleleni na?”"
  25,18,"Bayothi, “udumo malube kuwe! Kwakungasifanele ukuthi sithathe abanye abavikeli esikhundleni sakho kepha wena wabenza ukuthi bazithokozise kanye noyise kwaze kwaba yilapho bekhohlwa isexwayiso base bebangabantu abalahlekileyo”"
  25,19,Ngakho-ke bazokubiza ngamanga konke lokho enikushoyo bese ningabe nisakwazi ukuqhelelana (nesijeziso) futhi ningalutholi usizo futhi noma ngabe ngubani phakathi kwenu ongenabulungiswa simzwisa isijeziso esikhulu
  25,20,"Futhi asizange sithumele ngaphambilini kwakho isithunywa ngaphandle kokuthi zona zazikudla ukudla futhi ziya ezitolo futhi sabenza abanye benu ukuba yizilingo kwabanye, ngakube nizobekezela yini na? futhi iNkosi yakho ngasosonke isikhathi ibhekile"